Installation:

        git clone git://github.com/tompurl/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create Symlinks

        ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
        ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

git submodule add http://github.com/tpope/vim-fugitive.git bundle/fugitive-head
git push

git pull
git submodule init
git submodule update
